    "body": "This feature aims to support arbitrary page sizes in the FA4 forward kernel.\r\n\r\nThe current implementation adapts the implementation of paged attention from `paged_kv.h`.\r\n\r\nOptimizations not yet adapted:\r\n- Using thread 0 copy atom to resolve some values at compile-time\r\n- Sharded pointer computation + warp shuffle\r\n\r\n### Benchmarks\r\n\r\nPagesize 1\r\n```\r\nFlash Attention Benchmark:\r\n  num_kv_entries: 524288\r\n  page_size: 1\r\n  batch_size: 4\r\n  seqlen_q: 1\r\n  seqlen_k: 131072\r\n  nhead: 32\r\n  head_dim: 128\r\n  Arithmetic intensity: 0.999992370663676 FLOPS/byte\r\n  Avg time: 9.906083042557174 ms\r\n  TFLOPS: 0.867137349353633 TFLOPS\r\n  BW: 0.867143965086584 TB/s\r\nOutput matches reference\r\n```\r\n\r\nPagesize 32\r\n```\r\nFlash Attention Benchmark:\r\n  num_kv_entries: 524288\r\n  page_size: 32\r\n  batch_size: 4\r\n  seqlen_q: 1\r\n  seqlen_k: 131072\r\n  nhead: 32\r\n  head_dim: 128\r\n  Arithmetic intensity: 0.999992370663676 FLOPS/byte\r\n  Avg time: 6.344819207191467 ms\r\n  TFLOPS: 1.3538501746848566 TFLOPS\r\n  BW: 1.3538605037419753 TB/s\r\nOutput matches reference\r\n```\r\n\r\nPagesize 128 (baseline)\r\n```\r\nCommand: /usr/local/bin/python bench.py --page_size 128\r\nFlash Attention Benchmark:\r\n  num_kv_entries: 524288\r\n  page_size: 128\r\n  batch_size: 4\r\n  seqlen_q: 1\r\n  seqlen_k: 131072\r\n  nhead: 32\r\n  head_dim: 128\r\n  Arithmetic intensity: 0.999992370663676 FLOPS/byte\r\n  Avg time: 2.14695612095898 ms\r\n  TFLOPS: 4.000982837116922 TFLOPS\r\n  BW: 4.001013362193499 TB/s\r\nOutput matches reference\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Correctness\r\n\r\nStill need to support predicate for arbitrary head dim.\r\n\r\nPasses kvcache tests:\r\n```\r\n============================= test session starts ==============================\r\nplatform linux -- Python 3.12.1, pytest-9.0.1, pluggy-1.6.0\r\nrootdir: /root/flash_attn/tests\r\nconfigfile: pyproject.toml\r\ncollected 2784 items / 2400 deselected / 384 selected\r\n\r\n........ [  8%]\r\n..........................ssssssssssssssssssssssss....... [ 26%]\r\n........................................................................ [ 45%]\r\n.....ssssssssssss....................................................... [ 64%]\r\n.................ssssssssssssssssssssssss............................... [ 83%]\r\n.....................................................ssssssssssss        [100%]\r\n\r\n=============================== warnings summary ===============================\r\ncute/test_flash_attn.py: 1560 warnings\r\n  /usr/local/lib/python3.12/site-packages/nvidia_cutlass_dsl/python_packages/cutlass/base_dsl/_mlir_helpers/op.py:60: DeprecationWarning: `make_fragment` is deprecated, use `make_rmem_tensor` instead\r\n    res_or_list = opFunc(*args, **kwargs, loc=loc)\r\n\r\ncute/test_flash_attn.py: 15390 warnings\r\n  /usr/local/lib/python3.12/site-packages/nvidia_cutlass_dsl/python_packages/cutlass/base_dsl/_mlir_helpers/op.py:60: DeprecationWarning: cute.arch.exp2 is deprecated, use cute.math.exp2 with `fastmath=True` instead\r\n    res_or_list = opFunc(*args, **kwargs, loc=loc)\r\n\r\n-- Docs: https://docs.pytest.org/en/stable/how-to/capture-warnings.html\r\n= 312 passed, 72 skipped, 2400 deselected, 16950 warnings in 199.65s (0:03:19) =\r\n```",
